org.eclipse.dirigible.repository.api

Interface IRepository

  • All Superinterfaces:
    IRepositoryExporter, IRepositoryImporter, IRepositoryReader, IRepositorySearch, IRepositoryVersioning, IRepositoryWriter
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    DatabaseRepository, FileSystemMasterRepository, FileSystemRepository, JarMasterRepository, JarRepository, LocalRepository, ZipMasterRepository, ZipRepository

    public interface IRepository
extends IRepositoryReader, IRepositoryWriter, IRepositoryImporter, IRepositoryExporter, IRepositorySearch, IRepositoryVersioning
    This interface represents a Repository. It allows for querying, modifying and navigating through collections and resources.
